---
title: Southeast Asian Spiced Chicken with Roasted Pumpkin & Coconut-Lime Sauce
description: This simple, yet stunning meal is sure to amaze and delight. It's the perfect combination of tender chicken breast, an aromatic coconut-lime sauce and sweet roasted pumpkin.

*Unfortunately, this week's green beans were in short supply, so we've replaced them with broccoli. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5df0a0c1412fd55e5d2e52aa-a55abfe4.jpg
